  "texts": [
    "All the algorithms used are tested based on a set of parameters such as accuracy, sensitivity, and precision.",
    "Sulaiman et al. [26] represented various ML algorithms for CCFD and secure card holders' data.",
    "In order to increase the accuracy of FD and enhance privacy, their research suggests an effective hybrid model based on ML techniques, especially ANN.",
    "Similarly, Aziz and Ghous [27] investigated a range of DM approaches specifically designed to identify CCF, concentrating on several ML methodologies like RF, SVM, HM, DT, and DL.",
    "Based on previous actions, these techniques were used to determine typical customer behavior patterns."
  ]
